                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17171016-21-defend146 t17171016-21-deflabel118"></join>, and did work at the said Calling; and gave him a Character that made it look probable he had not followed this Practice long. However, the Jury found him <rs id="t17171016-21-verdict119" type="verdictDescription">
